@startuml sequence_followup_check
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence — Follow-Up Check and Cross-Reference

actor Candidate
participant "job-search Skill" as Skill
participant "recruiter-vendor-list.md" as RecruiterList
participant "target-accounts.md" as TargetAccounts

Candidate -> Skill : Run job-search or\ntrigger recruiter check
Skill -> RecruiterList : Read all recruiter records
RecruiterList --> Skill : Return RecruiterRecord list

Skill -> Skill : For each High-priority record:\ncompute days since last contact
Skill -> Skill : Collect records where\ndays >= 90 → overdue list

Skill -> TargetAccounts : Read target account list
TargetAccounts --> Skill : Return TargetAccount list

Skill -> Skill : Match firm names\n(case-insensitive) between\nrecruiter list and account list
Skill -> Skill : Flag unlinked matches\nas action items

Skill --> Candidate : Output "Due for follow-up" section\n(overdue High-priority contacts)\n+ Cross-reference action items

@enduml
